===== ZATACKA X =====
Zatacka X is a modern, Free remake of the classic Achtung, die Kurve!. In
addition to all the features from the original game, Zatacka X is aiming to
include better graphics, special weapons, sound effects, AI controlled
opponents, a tournament mode, and possibly online play.

More info to be found at https://github.com/simenheg/zatackax/.

===== INSTALLATION =====
For build instructions, see INSTALL.

